 8/10/18 St . Vast Our transport has not yet turn up owe to a railway smash but was report at Vignacourt at 10 a.m. so ought not to be long come across . An old Frenchman the owner of the hous where I am lodg woke me up this morn to present a cup of hot coffe . Charlesworth manag to get a dish of omellett and tea for me later . Dull raini and wretch today . Our Transport turn up just befor lunch . All the afternoon I was busi on Report on Operat on Honour Reward . We mess in the hous of a pretti littl widow . I inspect some of the billet ( they are not bad ) and yarn with all the old wive round the villag . Today
